globalblocking-blockedtext-ip:
{{optional}}
A message shown to a user whose IP is [[mw:Extension:GlobalBlocking|globally blocked]] when trying to edit.

Refers to:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-blockedtext-all-wikis}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-made-by}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-reason-comment}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-start-time}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-expiration-time}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-blockedtext-blocker-admin}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-blockedtext-email-feature}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-block-ip}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-include-details-queries}}

This message is similar to a [[MediaWiki:Blockedtext|MediaWiki core message]].

Parameters:
* $1 - The user to be executed
* $2 - The reason for the block
* $3 - The current IP address of the blocked user
* $4 - (Unused) the blocking sysop's username (plain text, without the link)
* $5 - The unique numeric identifier of the block
* $6 - The expiry of the block
* $8 - The timestamp when the block started

globalblocking-blockedtext-range:
{{optional}}
A message shown to a user whose IP is in a [[mw:Extension:GlobalBlocking|globally blocked]] range trying to edit.

Refers to
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-blockedtext-on-range}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-made-by}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-reason-comment}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-start-time}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-expiration-time}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-blockedtext-blocker-admin}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-blockedtext-email-feature}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-block-ip}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-blockedtext-ip-range}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-include-details-queries}}

Parameters:
* $1 - the blocking sysop (with a link to their user page if they are a local user)
* $2 - the reason for the block
* $3 - the current IP address of the blocked user
* $4 - (Unused) the blocking sysop's username (plain text, without the link)
* $5 - the unique numeric identifier of the block
* $6 - the expiry of the block
* $7 - the intended target of the block (what the blocking user specified in the blocking form)
* $8 - the timestamp when the block started

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-blockedtext-ip|notext=1}}

